<span >Tabletop Games</span><span >&nbsp;</span></h2><p>Tabletop Games Society is a friendly, open, free society that meets up most Wednesdays at 8PM in the bar in butler. We play any sort of table top game, from classics like monopoly and articulate, to more obscure games like citidels and powercore.</p><p>More infomation and session planning can be found at the facebook link below. Everything is organised through the facebook page.&nbsp;</p><p>Please have a look at the page and come along to the next session, you would be more than welcome.</p><p>We also try to do some larger events thoughout each term and the year, including game themed socials and 24hr gaming sessions, so keep an eye out for those too.</p><p>:D</p><p>group link :&nbsp;https://www.facebook.com/groups/203805103103291/</p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>